mobile games

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:50.120
with my daughter, who's seven.

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:53.030
So apps are really
transcending boundaries

00:03:53.030 --> 00:03:56.670
and defying our presumptions
of what users really like.

00:03:59.460 --> 00:04:01.980
And this is what makes
app promotion really hard.

00:04:01.980 --> 00:04:03.660
You're fishing for
the right users

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:05.960
who want to use your services.

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:09.780
