easier and more effective

00:04:09.780 --> 00:04:12.810
for you, we built a product
called Universal App

00:04:12.810 --> 00:04:16.380
Campaigns, or UAC.

00:04:16.380 --> 00:04:17.519
Now, what is UAC?

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:20.010
Very simply, it's
an ads product,

00:04:20.010 --> 00:04:22.980
and it helps you find the
right user for your app

00:04:22.980 --> 00:04:27.690
across multiple billion
user surfaces, including

00:04:27.690 --> 00:04:31.590
Google Search, the Google
Play Store, YouTube,

00:04:31.590 --> 00:04:35.340
and over three million sites and
apps across the Google Display

00:04:35.340 --> 00:04:36.870
Network.

