00:08:40.940 --> 00:08:44.330
And UAC uses machine
learning to learn

00:08:44.330 --> 00:08:47.210
which app users are the
most relevant and right

00:08:47.210 --> 00:08:48.680
for your app.

00:08:48.680 --> 00:08:51.300
And it does this by
combining, in real time,

00:08:51.300 --> 00:08:54.020
hundreds of millions
of signal combinations

00:08:54.020 --> 00:08:57.200
to understand where
the ad should show,

00:08:57.200 --> 00:09:00.470
who the ad should show to,
what the ad should look like,

00:09:00.470 --> 00:09:03.500
and also what to
pay for that ad.

00:09:03.500 --> 00:09:05.930
And it's doing all of this
optimization in real time

00:09:05.930 --> 00:09:08.570
to optimize the
value of your dollars

00:09:08.570 --> 00:09:11.720
so that we return the highest
ROI for your advertising

00:09:11.720 --> 00:09:13.400
budgets.

00:09:13.400 --> 00:09:16.940
And this helps you to
save both time and money

00:09:16.940 --> 00:09:18.860
