However, making ads informative
and engaging isn't enough.

00:11:41.300 --> 00:11:44.800
We also want to make them
super relevant for users.

00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:48.430
About 70% of users say that
they download an app based on

00:11:48.430 --> 00:11:51.050
whether they think they're
going to use it or not,

00:11:51.050 --> 00:11:53.920
which seems pretty
intuitive to me.

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:56.260
And so to help provide
more information

00:11:56.260 --> 00:11:59.230
about your app in
your install ads,

