we're introducing a new
feature, the ability

00:12:01.540 --> 00:12:05.650
to surface in-app content in
your Universal App Campaigns

00:12:05.650 --> 00:12:06.580
ads.

00:12:06.580 --> 00:12:09.700
Now, maybe an example is
more clear on explaining

00:12:09.700 --> 00:12:12.140
