through advertising.

00:14:50.340 --> 00:14:53.350
Now, getting ads into
your app may seem easy,

00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:56.980
but it's actually not that
obvious, and here's why.

00:14:56.980 --> 00:14:59.010
Number one is what I
